# Plan 7: Homepage Hero & Featured Content

## Goal
Design a stunning homepage with a full-screen hero section and featured content.

## Tasks
- [ ] Create `app/page.tsx`.
- [ ] Design the Hero section:
    - [ ] Large background image/video.
    - [ ] **ShadCN Button** (size="lg") for "Listen Now" CTA.
    - [ ] (Optional) Use **ShadCN Carousel** for rotating featured content.
- [ ] Create "Featured Music" section:
    - [ ] Use `ReleaseCard` (from Plan 5).
- [ ] Create "Latest News" section.
- [ ] Implement parallax scrolling (Framer Motion).
- [ ] Use `glass-panel` utility for any text overlays.
